welcome to ZtickFish! Our goal is to help you understand films better while adding a fun and entertaining twist to each video.

Each video we make takes around 1 day to make, and we got a team of 2 people.
Hereâ€™s how we do it:

First, we pick a movie that we think youâ€™ll find intriguing or exciting.
then we find the best/most entertaining clips of that movie and put it in our software called after effects.
then we chose a song that matches the movie/energy perfect.

then we add text, and each text has different effects/fonts/color to match the vocals of the actor.
then we add effects/transistions/zooms/Flashes/Sound effects/watermark/
